s by listening and working together with each individual that comes to him. He provides a relaxing, safe, and comfortable space to help you reinforce or develop the relationships between your mind, body, and spirit. Which results in stress relief, pain reduction, improved flexibility, mental clarity, emotional well-being and empowerment of your body.","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"11b134de-1089-4cca-841c-203d8b208c56","name":"Christy Mulvey","image":"https://www.lomilomikona.com/image/40410945.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage, Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing","modalities":["Massage","Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"By visiting this website you've taken your first step towards health and healing. Please feel free to look around the site to learn about what I have to offer. And when you're ready to begin your transformation, Call or Text me and we'll set up your first appointment.","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.610086,"lng":-155.975429,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"eafde5c0-cb5e-4755-a0d4-b8f5e821ef7f","name":"Colon Hydrotherapy with Silke","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage, Alternative Therapy","modalities":["Massage","Alternative Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"","location":"Pahoa","rating":5,"lat":19.481924,"lng":-154.944083,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4fee7363-9dcc-4404-8e6f-40ff939b1f7c","name":"Dawn Adele Mobile Massage LLC","image":"https://avatar.setmore.com/files/public/f2fI02EiIkvF/waterfall-pic.jpeg?crop=1536%3B512%3B0%3B588&format=png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Aloha, I'm Dawn, a Hawaii licensed massage therapist. I come to you, offering therapeutic massages which will ease tension & muscle soreness while relaxing and renewing you. I provide an extra wide massage table with every massage tailored to your specific needs. I service Waikoloa Beach resort, Waikoloa Village, Mauna Lani, Manu Kea, Kawaihae & Waimea areas. Choose the type of massage you want, length of time, day and time of day. Add reflexology, hot stones, cupping or aromatherapy to enhance your massage experience ( additional charges, must let me know in advance) NOTE: If less than 24 hour notification…","location":"Waikoloa","rating":5,"lat":19.93797,"lng":-155.791084,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:40.073062+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"c287599f-2019-46d3-81a7-80ebcd0a2d88","name":"Craig Cain - Kiso Method","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic, Acupuncture, Massage, Alternative Therapy","modalities":["Chiropractic","Acupuncture","Massage","Alternative Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Find relief and healing at Awakening Healing Center in Hilo, Hawai'i. We offer chiropractic care, massage therapy, acupuncture, Vax-D, physical therapy, and veterans' services, all using the unique Kiso Method. Schedule your appointment today!","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.726014,"lng":-155.088223,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"713d633c-1ce2-4f70-a794-52ed3e5fa902","name":"The Goal.","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/65d8161ed7be7b012d24f809/t/65f271f5dd3993160e181a1b/1710387705819/OHIA+LOGO.jpg?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage, Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing","modalities":["Massage","Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":t