 30 years, Jill Henderson has dedicated her career to helping people move better, feel stronger, and live with less pain. She specializes in deep tissue and sports rehabilitation massage tailored to meet each client’s needs. Whether you're an athlete recovering from injury, or simply seeking improved movement and balance, my goal is to help you heal and thrive.","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.028772,"lng":-155.667198,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"7e287a2b-e917-4dfe-a2cd-d5394aa798fa","name":"Why Choose Us","businessName":"NIU Hawaii, LLC","image":"https://niuhawaiillc.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/123123124-e1770898804894.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"With 20 years of clinical experience as a 3rd-generation licensed massage therapist (MAT-9551), I am deeply committed to guiding my clients toward optimal health and vitality. I believe true healing is found in the harmony between professional expertise and the deep-rooted ancestral wisdom of my lineage.","location":"Keaau","rating":5,"lat":19.592183,"lng":-155.069101,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"06432bb6-6b10-4477-869e-335a9d94e3c9","name":"Kayla Mei Massage","image":"https://images.msha.ke/f3bf1aaa-98a3-4582-beaf-400deed772ca?w=1200&ar=2%3A1&crop=faces%2Centropy%2Ccenter&fit=crop&fm=png&auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=tinysrgb&q=30","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Kayla Mei Acasio","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":19.619734,"lng":-155.949247,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"0d1c6d0e-be1f-4101-a301-b918cc7cd075","name":"Main Content","image":