","verified":false},{"id":"d8cb55ca-5e11-4bfa-ad12-b9f43e892982","name":"Lomilomi Hawaiian Massage","image":"http://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/stock/2719","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Experience the best in massage therapy at Malama Honua Massage Therapy. Book your Lomilomi wellness therapy appointment today!","location":"Papaikou","rating":5,"lat":19.814873,"lng":-155.10095,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"0e5051aa-71e4-4aca-a2de-7b829c301b73","name":"Margaret Eyles","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/c7b72ff7d50be646055092ee60bfb5a0.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage, Somatic Therapy, Craniosacral","modalities":["Massage","Somatic Therapy","Craniosacral"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Margaret became a certified Rolfer® in 1988 and a Certified Rolf Movement® Teacher in 1995, and later achieved my Advance Rolfing certification. In addition to that training she is also a certified massage therapist and has trained in Cranial-Sacral Therapy. She believes in educating her clients so that they may develop their inherent ability to heal themselves, for they are the best authority regarding their physical well-being. Margaret lives in Holualoa near Kona on the Big Island of Hawaii and finds refuge in the sea as both a swimmer and free diver. She was exposed to the healing arts at…","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"e4336203-2f95-4a98-a7c7-dd04afb1b709","name":"Marlene Sperka - Tao Of The Body","businessName":"Tao Of The Body","image":"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/stock/2734","type":"practitioner","modality":"Life Coaching, Massage","modalities":["Life Coaching","Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Founded by Marlene Sperka, LMT, AHC (MAE 1844, MAT 6128) Tao Of The Body blends medical massage therapy with Ayurvedic principles to support whole-body healing.  With over two decades of experience, Marlene specializes in therapeutic bodywork addressing pain, structural imbalance and nervous system regulation while honoring the mind-body connection.","location":"Kailua Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.604524,"lng":-155.962211,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"97c9bc79-1b49-4766-85dd-59dc75999476","name":"Massage 808-329-0060","image":"https://massagewaikoloa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/iStock_000003711019XSmall.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Did you schedule a massage in Waikoloa, Hawaii? If you haven't done it before you should place it on your listing of activities to do.","location":"Waikoloa","rating":5,"lat":19.540669,"lng":-155.929279,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"5ec9baf7-ddeb-498e-9a0f-8fec783dc131","name":"Matia Jones Massage","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/a04b33_0be8003e238349a3882431f8a6ed6ff4~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_243,h_265,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/a04b33_0be8003e238349a3882431f8a6ed6ff4~mv2.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Licensed since 2003, Matia has accumulated many techniques, insights, and tools through both formal educational as well as through hands-on experience. Her massage work incorporates multiple modalities, drawing most heavily from  Swedish, Lomi Lomi, Cranio Sacral, Deep Tissue,  and  Trauma-Informed Bodywork . Meditation and somatics also provide foundational elements to her practice.","location":"Keaau","rating":5,"lat":19.618077,"lng":-154.948391,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4b292131-e166-472f-93b2-863e85b5e390","name":"Mauna Lani Chiropractic","businessName":"Mauna Lani Chiropractic","image":"http://www.maunalanichiropractic.com/client-portal-api/practice-website-uploads/210758","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic, Massage","modalities":["Chiropractic","Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Chiropractic in Kamuela, HI offering Chiropractic services. Paperwork can be filled out online. Schedule an appointment today. ","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":19.941648,"lng":-155.858465,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"79d48c21-e235-4d27-a369-012298a2245a","name":"Mickayla Monson","image":"https://www.malamachiropractic.com/wp-content/uploads/bb-plugin/cache/Chiropractor-Kailua-Kona-HI-Jesse-Broderson-circle.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Chiropractic Care begins with finding a great chiropractor. In Kailua-Kona residents and visitors have a lot of choices- what makes Malama Chiropractic Clinic stand out in our community is that we follow The Golden Rule - we treat our patients how we would want to be treated. To us, this means listening to our patients, finding and treating the real cause of their pain or concern. It’s why all treatments start with a short massage and end with time to lie down and relax. It’s why we have assembled a team of knowledgeable staff and caring Kailua-Kona HI chiropractors to…","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"358f087f-d044-4532-8027-20d682db4b0b","name":"Mieko Henderson - Inline Rolfing","businessName":"Inline Rolfing","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/avatars/1772148511797_249m6l89f03.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Structural Integration Practitioner, Massage","modalities":["Structural Integration Practitioner","Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Welcome to Inline Rolfing, where we offer professional and transformative structural integration services that will leave you feeling aligned and rejuvenated.","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.7241,"lng":-155.0868,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"19848521-a86f-44d0-8e4d-32dd68fffae2","name":"Nancy Campbell","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/practitioners/1775428982085-t745033e4qe.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage, Reiki","modalities":["Massage","Reiki"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Nancy has been practicing massage and bodywork since 2004. She provides Medical Massage, CranioSacral, Myofascial work, SMRT, NRT, and Reiki to bring you an integrated session that is custom to your needs. Nobody deserves to be in pain.","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.719928,"lng":-155.087358,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-05T23:20:09.929408+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"2b489cd4-3651-492a-b49c-c6937f888267","name":"Napa Thai Massage","image":"https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/6210820d-bdf9-42d4-93e3-15e2f779b62f/napa_thai_massage_1080w_enhanced.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Revitalize your body and mind with expert massage services.\nBy Appointment Only","location":"Hilo","rati