s of the body. There are several  different types of massage techniques including: Hawaiian Lomi Lomi, Swedish, Deep Tissue Point Thereapy, Shiatsu, Sports Massage, and Reflexology.  Massage is used to relieve stress, increase blood flow, soothe aches and pain, relax tense muscles, and increase the general well-being of the body.","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.604837,"lng":-155.962419,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"eae13535-1732-49cb-b7fd-9b11deb7264e","name":"Tiare Room Service Massage","image":"https://tiaremassage.com/aloha/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Tiarelogowithimage646x600.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Tiare Room Service Massage provides on location (we come to you) massage services.","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"2273a91f-d8a9-4b3e-bfbc-c5263f722e57","name":"Tina Pliura-Mohr","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/practitioners/1775026409441-7exg3gazo.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Massage, Craniosacral","modalities":["Massage","Craniosacral"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Tina is a highly skilled practitioner with over 35 years of experience specializing in injury care and restorative bodywork. Caring, competent and compassionate, Tina offers a variety of foundational and advanced bodywork modalities as a true healer.","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:39.217838+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"11177a96-8478-43dd-b2ec-cdd83f5f1fd9","name":"Tina Pliura-Mohr LMT / Massage Therapy","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality"