 why we utilize a variety of therapeutic modalities such as acupuncture, massage, simple structural guidance, herbal formulas, and access to fresh nutritional foods to stimulate your body’s inherent ability to repair and restore vitality. ","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"ae9e02bb-513f-46e5-a0f1-17819f1c7b2a","name":"Gingerhill Farm Retreat","image":"https://gingerhillfarm.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Homepage_Accommodations_Image1.png","modality":"Massage, Yoga, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Massage","Yoga","Nature Therapy"],"location":"Kealakekua","rating":5,"lat":19.50394,"lng":-155.926358,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Eat delicious, healing farm-to-fork food. Get intimate with nature and find your unadulterated self. We would love to see you at our Hawaii retreat.","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"0d817278-7634-4889-a131-bd71aa3bf844","name":"Glow Raw World Skin Spa","image":"https://glowrawworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo_1.png","modality":"Massage","modalities":["Massage"],"location":"Kealakekua","rating":5,"lat":19.512768,"lng":-155.921602,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"A sanctuary offering organic facials, body treatments, and spiritual ceremonies. Revitalize your inner and outer beauty with our holistic approach to wellness. Book your transformative experience today.","centerType":"spa","centerTypeLabel":"Spa","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"096e0b8e-19d9-46f4-bdf7-feefe46018e5","name":"Hale Lomilomi o Kekaimalino","image":"https://img1.wsimg.com/iste